  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK717">
<l>kaṟṟaṟintār kalvi viḷaṅkuṅ kacaṭaṟac</l>
<l>coṟṟeriya vallā rakattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learning of those who have read and understood (much) will shine in the assembly of those who faultlessly examine (the nature of) words.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
